name: FHFC | Boo Lifetime Mint Pass
description: The FHFC Boo Lifetime Mint Passes are LTD edition WL passes that give a (Guaranteed Allocation) of 25% on all the WL spots for every FHFC NFT Drop! If you collect all 11 Unique Editions you can burn them to redeem a MEGA BOO. There will only ever be 100 MEGA BOOs created.
